text: Abramtsevo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Khotkovo Urban Settlement of Sergiyevo-Posadsky District, Moscow Oblast, Russia. The population was 209 as of 2010. There are 44 streets.Улицы села Абрамцево == References == Category:Rural localities in Moscow Oblast
title: Abramtsevo, Sergiyevo-Posadsky District, Moscow Oblast
